::KitKat2::

She looked at FZ and growled. "WHo are you? And what do you mean 
back? When was I hear?"  She walked past him and started looking 
around.  "Hmm, this doesn't seam familiar."  She could smell her 
scent everywhere. It was unnerving to smell your own scent trail, but 
have no memory that you were ever there.  She looked at FZ and 
transformed into bot mode.  "You said back here?  When was I here 
before? I don't get it?"  She shook her head, "Eh, don't worry about 
it then. Where's the mess hall? I'm starving."
